  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nBased on the https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/11969 ticket, when we have a community ownership change, all users will be kicked and a new owner will wait until they share their revealed addresses and accept them automatically\r\n\r\nRight now such users will be shown in the pending state of the community membership changes.\r\nThe idea is to show them in a separate tab\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/117639195/d8c0f3d6-5cf2-416b-a073-f0a12f2524e2)\r\n\r\n\r\n",
