    "body": "@benjthayer All members, including admins and token masters, will be kicked (only the new owner will stay). After auto-rejoin they will receive their roles according to the community permission settings (must be the same roles, if the new owner didn't change anything).\r\n\r\nHow it will look like on a high level:\r\n1. The owner receives an ownership token and sets himself as a control node of the community\r\n2. All members will be kicked as the new owner requires revealed addresses from all community members\r\n3. Clients will detect, that the ownership changed and send their request to join for auto-rejoin\r\n4. Onwer sees that this user was a member of the community previously and auto accepts him, setting a necessary role based on the community token permissions and revealed address\r\n\r\n",
